    "html": "<div class=\"container\"><h1 class=\"main-title\">Einiosaurus pictures and facts</h1>\n\n      <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"main-content col-sm-6\">\n          <div class=\"intro\">\n            <div class=\"img-container dino-page-featured\">\n              <span><img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus_00657d2b.jpg\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <p>\n              Einiosaurus was a <strong>herbivore</strong>.  It lived in the <span><strong>Cretaceous</strong></span> period and inhabited <strong>North America</strong>.\n                Its fossils have been found in places such as <span>Montana</span>.\n\n            </p>\n            <p>\n              \n            </p>\n            <p>\n              Quick facts about Einiosaurus:\n              <ul>\n                <li>Existed from 83.6 million years ago to 72.1 million years ago</li>\n\n                <li>Lived in a terrestrial habitat</li>\n\n                <li>Was a herbivore</li>\n\n                <li>Reproduced by laying eggs</li>\n\n\n\n\n                  <li>3 different specimens have been found by paleontologists</li>\n              </ul>\n              \n            </p>\n            <p>\n            All the Einiosaurus illustrations below were collected from the internet.  Enjoy and explore:\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          \n<div class=\"info-section references\">\n  Einiosaurus was described by the following scientific paper(s):\n  <ul>\n      <li>D. J. Varricchio. 2001. Late Cretaceous oviraptorosaur (Theropoda) dinosaurs from Montana. D. H. Tanke and K. Carpenter (eds.), Mesozoic Vertebrate Life, Indiana University Press, Bloomington </li>\n      <li>R. R. Rogers. 1991. Taphonomy of three dinosaur bone beds in the Upper Cretaceous Two Medicine Formation of Northwestern Monana: evidence for drought-related mortality. Palaios 5:394-413</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"right-side col-sm-5\">\n          <div class=\"map-container\">\n            <div class=\"map-image-container\">\n              <img width=\"426\" height=\"320\" id=\"map-image\" src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/map.jpg\" alt=\"Locations where Einiosaurus fossils were found.\" title=\"Locations where Einiosaurus fossils were found.\">\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"under-map-container\">\n              <p>\n                <em>Location of Einiosaurus fossils.</em>\n              </p>\n              <p class=\"prev-next-dino\">\n                <span>&laquo; Eiectus</span>\n                &middot;\n\n                <strong>Einiosaurus</strong>\n\n                &middot;\n                <span>Ekrixinatosaurus &raquo;</span>\n              </p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"globe-container\">\n              \n              <div class=\"view-on-globe\"><span>⧉ Full globe</span></div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div id=\"images\" class=\"pics\">\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus_00657d2b.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus_bf2deca5.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n        \n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus-4_cace.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus-dinosaur-artwork-sciepro_864a.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/horns05__einiosaurus_by_tuomaskoivurinne-d2svej7_1b22.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus_l_c636.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus_d9d2.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus_jpg_cab3.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus_bw_9d02.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus_d7f9.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus__15__by_wolverine041269-d5z77tf_bb48.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus_portrait_1280_a26c.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus-2_fc29.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus_644f.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus-size_ebb1.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus_120c.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus1_5a6b.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus_eco_e108.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus-daz-05a_0001_e99e.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus-daz-02b_0001_b8c2.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/einiosaurus/einiosaurus-daz-01a_0001_5f76.jpg\" title=\"Einiosaurus\" alt=\"Einiosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n      </div></div>",
