    "title": "Tsintaosaurus",
    "sourceUrl": "https://dinosaurpictures.org/Tsintaosaurus-pictures",
    "html": "<div class=\"container\"><h1 class=\"main-title\">Tsintaosaurus pictures and facts</h1>\n\n      <div class=\"row\">\n        <div class=\"main-content col-sm-6\">\n          <div class=\"intro\">\n            <div class=\"img-container dino-page-featured\">\n              <span><img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus_a5a9c316.jpg\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <p>\n              Tsintaosaurus was a <strong>herbivore</strong>.  It lived in the <span><strong>Cretaceous</strong></span> period and inhabited <strong>Asia</strong>.\n                Its fossils have been found in places such as <span>Shandong (China)</span>.\n\n            </p>\n            <p>\n              \n            </p>\n            <p>\n              Quick facts about Tsintaosaurus:\n              <ul>\n                <li>Existed from 83.6 million years ago to 72.1 million years ago</li>\n\n                <li>Lived in a terrestrial habitat</li>\n\n                <li>Was a herbivore</li>\n\n                <li>Reproduced by laying eggs</li>\n\n\n\n\n                  <li>4 different specimens have been found by paleontologists</li>\n              </ul>\n              \n            </p>\n            <p>\n            All the Tsintaosaurus illustrations below were collected from the internet.  Enjoy and explore:\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          \n<div class=\"info-section references\">\n  Tsintaosaurus was described by the following scientific paper(s):\n  <ul>\n      <li>C.-C. Young. 1958. The dinosaurian remains of Laiyang, Shantung. Palaeontologia Sinica, New Series C, Whole Number 42(16):1-138</li>\n      <li>C.-C. Young and C.-y. Wang. 1959. [On a new excavation of dinosaurs in Laiyang, Shantung]. Palaeovertebrata et Paleoanthropologia 1(1):53-54</li>\n  </ul>\n</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"right-side col-sm-5\">\n          <div class=\"map-container\">\n            <div class=\"map-image-container\">\n              <img width=\"426\" height=\"320\" id=\"map-image\" src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/map.jpg\" alt=\"Locations where Tsintaosaurus fossils were found.\" title=\"Locations where Tsintaosaurus fossils were found.\">\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"under-map-container\">\n              <p>\n                <em>Location of Tsintaosaurus fossils.</em>\n              </p>\n              <p class=\"prev-next-dino\">\n                <span>&laquo; Tsagantegia</span>\n                &middot;\n\n                <strong>Tsintaosaurus</strong>\n\n                &middot;\n                <span>Tsogtopteryx &raquo;</span>\n              </p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"globe-container\">\n              \n              <div class=\"view-on-globe\"><span>⧉ Full globe</span></div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div id=\"images\" class=\"pics\">\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus_a5a9c316.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus_8226324e.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n\n        \n        \n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      \n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus_by_dinowrassler620-d74rdcf_8645.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/mm-tsintaosaurus-illustration-big_d255.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus_by_adamzt2-d4w963k_d8b9.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus-pietro-antognioni_b66a.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus_fc5e.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      \n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus_squelette_5cee.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus_2b08.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus_14d7.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus-spinorhinus-sergey-krasovskiy_4511.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus-m.shiraishi_bcda.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus_spinorhinus_by_atrox1-d6yvzjv_fb37.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus_8e89.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus_by_ntamura-d6zhtsj_b620.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurusdb_3ee8.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus-size_3842.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus_by_vitor_silva-d6v8kej_adae.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n<div class=\"img-container\">\n  \n  \n  <span>\n      <img src=\"data/images/dinosaur-pictures/tsintaosaurus/tsintaosaurus_01_9df9.jpg\" title=\"Tsintaosaurus\" alt=\"Tsintaosaurus\">\n  </span>\n  \n  \n  \n</div>\n      </div></div>",
